107
00:07:03,319 --> 00:07:05,339
sooner or later.

108
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:08,333
It's all right, Old Jin.

109
00:07:08,333 --> 00:07:10,519
Don't worry about it.

110
00:07:19,418 --> 00:07:22,580
[Episode 29: Flying Against the Wind]

111
00:07:22,580 --> 00:07:27,140
Ellipses and hyperbolas would certainly be the final big question in the college entrance exam and difficulty points.

112
00:07:27,140 --> 00:07:30,219
Everyone must clearly understand these types of questions.

113
00:07:30,219 --> 00:07:31,600
Is there anything else you don't understand?

114
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,760
Yes.

115
00:07:32,760 --> 00:07:33,859
Which problem? I'll explain it to you.

116
00:07:33,859 --> 00:07:35,917
All of them.

117
00:07:37,299 --> 00:07:40,800
Sorry, Xiaowen. We're too stupid.

118
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,577
It's okay.

119
00:07:45,170 --> 00:07:47,900
Why don't we go get ice cream?

120
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,720
W-we're not studying anymore?

121
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:53,320
We should balance work and rest. We need to relax a little, too.

122
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:55,600
Let's go. I'll go get Tian Meng.

123
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,471
Here.

124
00:08:05,539 --> 00:08:06,279
Beibei.

125
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:08,072
