128
00:08:17,219 --> 00:08:19,720
Really? Did I change for the better or the worse?

129
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:21,506
You're stronger now.

130
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,779
Xiaowen,

131
00:08:26,779 --> 00:08:30,500
