132
00:08:30,500 --> 00:08:32,341
force...

133
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:34,880
f-for...

134
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:36,970
- force yourself to look happy.
- That's right.

135
00:08:37,779 --> 00:08:39,279
