♫ The sunshine that year was great ♫

216
00:14:23,639 --> 00:14:27,420
Gao Yang used to say I muddled along at school.

217
00:14:28,220 --> 00:14:30,852
Now that everyone approves of me,

218
00:14:31,699 --> 00:14:33,795
he's not here to see it.

219
00:14:36,159 --> 00:14:40,159
We'll go to Beijing and tell him in person.

220
00:14:41,779 --> 00:14:47,972
Xiaowen, let your name resound through the skies in Beijing.

221
00:14:51,950 --> 00:14:58,120
[Tieyuan Station]

222
00:15:05,799 --> 00:15:09,228
Mi Jia, Xiaowen, you've never been to Beijing, right?

223
00:15:09,228 --> 00:15:11,559
When the competition is over, I'll show you around the city.

224
00:15:11,559 --> 00:15:12,440
Where do you want to go?

225
00:15:12,440 --> 00:15:15,279
Tian'anmen, the Great Wall, the Forbidden City!

226
00:15:15,279 --> 00:15:17,659
Wait, why are you guys here?

227
00:15:17,659 --> 00:15:19,559
- Beibei, did you sneak out?
- No, no.

228
00:15:19,559 --> 00:15:22,899
- I will call Old Jin.
- No, no. My dad agreed to let me come this time.

229
00:15:22,899 --> 00:15:26,580
