- I told my mom I'm going to visit colleges in Beijing.

230
00:15:26,580 --> 00:15:29,879
- Jiabao?
- I'm going to watch the competition and cheer for them.

231
00:15:32,220 --> 00:15:36,459
Uncle Gao, will Gao Yang be there?

232
00:15:37,140 --> 00:15:38,775
Gao Yang...

233
00:15:39,519 --> 00:15:41,240
He can do whatever he wants.

234
00:15:41,240 --> 00:15:45,379
The most important thing is to cheer for Xiaowen and Mi Jia, understand?

235
00:15:45,939 --> 00:15:49,480
I left him a message. He'll come for sure.

236
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:54,800
Obey my orders in the venue. Don't run about.

237
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:56,000
- Okay.
- All right.

238
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:59,080
Let's set off for Beijing!

239
00:15:59,080 --> 00:16:01,300
- Let's go!
- Let's go!

240
00:16:04,720 --> 00:16:07,559
Alright, the next word is "nostalgia".

241
00:16:07,559 --> 00:16:09,940
