249
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:37,960
- Okay.
- Okay.

250
00:16:37,960 --> 00:16:39,499
- See you next time.
- See you.

251
00:16:39,499 --> 00:16:41,478
- Bye-bye.
- Bye.

252
00:16:43,360 --> 00:16:44,819
Teacher, is class over?

253
00:16:44,819 --> 00:16:46,039
Yes.

254
00:16:46,039 --> 00:16:47,440
How is he doing lately?

255
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:48,419
Pretty good.

256
00:16:48,419 --> 00:16:50,579
Really? Thank you for your hard work.

257
00:16:50,579 --> 00:16:52,480
Take it easy. Thank you.

258
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:54,519
You're welcome. Bye-bye.

259
00:16:54,519 --> 00:16:57,639
Son, good job.

260
00:16:57,639 --> 00:17:01,139
The teacher complimented you and said you improved.

261
00:17:01,639 --> 00:17:05,859
Mom, I want to take a day off and go walk around.

262
00:17:05,859 --> 00:17:07,440
Sure. When?

263
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:09,211
Tomorrow.

264
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:11,160
I forgot to tell you.

265
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:12,920
We're going to get our visas tomorrow.

266
00:17:12,920 --> 00:17:15,319
We can only do it tomorrow?

267
00:17:15,319 --> 00:17:17,320
I already made an appointment for tomorrow.

268
00:17:17,320 --> 00:17:19,381
What is it? Do you need to do something?

269
00:17:20,720 --> 00:17:22,323
No.

270
00:17:43,294 --> 00:17:45,239
[National High School Long-Distance Race]

271
00:17:52,914 --> 00:17:55,340
Xiaowen, don't be nervous later.

272
00:17:55,340 --> 00:17:56,759
Just perform normally.

273
00:17:56,759 --> 00:17:59,419
As long as you are within the top 3 places, you can get into the Beijing University of Technology.

274
00:17:59,419 --> 00:18:01,540
Don't worry, Mr. Gao.

275
00:18:02,100 --> 00:18:02,880
Come on.

276
00:18:02,880 --> 00:18:04,428
Xiaowen.

277
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:08,039
We were opponents in Tieyuan.

278
00:18:08,039 --> 00:18:11,020
Out here, we're brothers in arms. Don't bring shame to Tieyuan.

279
00:18:11,020 --> 00:18:12,699
You too. Good luck.

280
00:18:12,699 --> 00:18:16,819
All athletes, report to the call room.

281
00:18:16,819 --> 00:18:19,120
- Good luck.
- Good luck.

282
00:18:21,119 --> 00:18:24,140
Xiaowen, good luck.

283
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:31,720
Xiaowen, good luck! Xiaowen, good luck!

284
00:18:31,720 --> 00:18:36,839
Xiaowen, good luck! Xiaowen, good luck! Xiaowen, good luck!

285
00:18:36,839 --> 00:18:38,920
Xiaowen, good luck!

286
00:18:38,920 --> 00:18:44,079
Xiaowen, good luck! Xiaowen, good luck! Xiaowen, good luck!

287
00:18:44,079 --> 00:18:46,639
Xiaowen, good luck!

288
00:18:56,000 --> 00:18:57,848
What's wrong?

289
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:04,300
Mom, how long will it take to apply for the visa?

290
00:19:04,300 --> 00:19:07,080
Not sure. Sometimes it's fast and sometimes it's slow.

291
00:19:07,080 --> 00:19:08,739
What's the matter?

292
00:19:08,739 --> 00:19:10,520
It's nothing.

293
00:19:12,599 --> 00:19:14,079
I need to buy a reference book.

294
00:19:14,079 --> 00:19:16,800
Sure, we'll do that after.

295
00:19:19,419 --> 00:19:21,780
Jia, when are you competing?

296
00:19:21,780 --> 00:19:23,719
Tomorrow.

297
00:19:23,719 --> 00:19:26,680
It'll all come down to Xiaowen today.

298
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:28,519
Where's Gao Yang?

299
00:19:28,519 --> 00:19:30,519
I can't find him.

300
00:19:30,519 --> 00:19:32,839
Bei, look carefully.

301
00:19:32,839 --> 00:19:34,480
Look... look over there.

302
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:36,720
I already looked over there.

303
00:19:36,720 --> 00:19:39,480
He's not over there either.

304
00:19:41,459 --> 00:19:44,060
Uncle Gao, over here!

305
00:19:45,540 --> 00:19:47,813
I'm sorry. Excuse me.

306
00:19:49,440 --> 00:19:52,359
Uncle Gao, why aren't you watching down there?

307
00:19:52,359 --> 00:19:53,519
I have to keep an eye on you guys.

308
00:19:53,519 --> 00:19:54,960
What if you guys run about?

309
00:19:54,960 --> 00:19:57,683
No way.

310
00:19:57,683 --> 00:20:00,040
Mr. Gao, how is Xiaowen's condition?

311
00:20:00,839 --> 00:20:03,079
Don't worry, it's quite good.

312
00:20:08,659 --> 00:20:13,020
Beibei, well, did you see Gao Yang?

313
00:20:13,020 --> 00:20:14,867
No.

314
00:20:14,867 --> 00:20:18,040
I told you his mom wouldn't let him come.

315
00:20:20,459 --> 00:20:22,609
Let me borrow your binoculars.

316
00:20:28,540 --> 00:20:32,790
[Exceed Yourself]

317
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:51,640
On your marks.

318
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:53,311
Get set.

319
00:20:56,280 --> 00:20:58,180
[Tieyuan No. 3 High's Xiaowen is the best]

320
00:21:04,490 --> 00:21:07,100
♫  I want to go to the future  ♫

321
00:21:07,100 --> 00:21:10,680
Go! Xiaowen, go!

322
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:13,160
- Xiaowen, go!
- Go!

323
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:18,960
Go, Xiaowen! Go, Xiaowen!

324
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:22,400
Go, Xiaowen! Go, Xiaowen!

325
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:24,079
Go, Xiaowen!

326
00:21:24,079 --> 00:21:29,359
Go, Xiaowen! Go, Xiaowen!

327
00:21:29,359 --> 00:21:34,079
Go, Xiaowen! Go, Xiaowen!

328
00:21:34,079 --> 00:21:37,000
- Go, Xiaowen!
- Go! Go!

329
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:40,359
Go, go, go!

330
00:21:40,359 --> 00:21:41,759
Go, Xiaowen!

331
00:21:41,759 --> 00:21:45,560
Go, go, go!

332
00:21:45,560 --> 00:21:47,659
Mom, can I go buy the book now?
[Beijing Municipal of Public Security Exit and Entry Administration]

333
00:21:47,659 --> 00:21:49,900
I'll come back right after I buy it.

334
00:21:49,900 --> 00:21:51,000
I'll take you there.

335
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:54,000
No need, I can go by myself. I know the way.

336
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:56,485
It's faster to take the car. Come on.

337
00:21:56,485 --> 00:21:57,924
Mom,

338
00:21:59,400 --> 00:22:01,540
I'm not going to buy a book.

339
00:22:01,540 --> 00:22:03,680
Xiaowen is in Beijing.

340
00:22:03,680 --> 00:22:06,259
I want to go and watch his competition.

341
00:22:07,319 --> 00:22:09,062
I knew it.

342
00:22:10,659 --> 00:22:13,000
You don't seem right recently.

343
00:22:13,799 --> 00:22:15,939
- Please let me go, Mom.
- No.

344
00:22:15,939 --> 00:22:20,840
Mom, I'll come back as soon as I know the results of the competition.

345
00:22:20,840 --> 00:22:22,860
I don't even have to see them.

346
00:22:22,860 --> 00:22:24,683
You mean it?

347
00:22:24,683 --> 00:22:26,359
I mean it.

348
00:22:32,560 --> 00:22:35,854
Will you stop resisting me from now on?

349
00:22:35,854 --> 00:22:37,898
Yes.

350
00:22:37,898 --> 00:22:40,879
Uncle Gao, what place is Xiaowen in now?

351
00:22:40,879 --> 00:22:43,959
Xiaowen is in the first tier. The leading athletes are all pretty strong.

352
00:22:43,959 --> 00:22:45,160
They almost overlapped the rest by two laps.

353
00:22:45,160 --> 00:22:47,340
- Really? That's great.
- Yes.

354
00:22:47,340 --> 00:22:49,240
Xiaowen fell!

355
00:22:54,859 --> 00:22:56,119
- Xiaowen!
- Xiaowen!

356
00:22:56,119 --> 00:22:57,720
- Xiaowen!
- Stand up!

357
00:22:57,720 --> 00:23:00,340
- Xiaowen.
- Xiaowen, stand up!

358
00:23:09,700 --> 00:23:11,359
Compensate me. Hurry up and compensate me!

359
00:23:11,359 --> 00:23:13,319
Who should be the one compensating? Look at how you crashed into my car!

360
00:23:13,319 --> 00:23:14,780
You... you... Why were you in such a hurry?

361
00:23:14,780 --> 00:23:17,634
- How did you back up the car?
- How much money would I make a day?

362
00:23:55,839 --> 00:23:59,259
Xiaowen, stand up.

363
00:24:00,019 --> 00:24:02,739
Stand up, Xiaowen.

364
00:24:02,739 --> 00:24:04,900
Xiaowen, get up.

365
00:25:00,680 --> 00:25:03,165
Hurry up and turn around! I'm running late!

366
00:26:03,880 --> 00:26:05,240
Young man, what are you doing?

367
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:06,440
This is the exit.

368
00:26:06,440 --> 00:26:08,531
The competition is over a while ago.

369
00:26:09,259 --> 00:26:11,540
Do you know what place was Ye Xiaowen?

370
00:26:11,540 --> 00:26:13,720
How would I know?

371
00:26:14,419 --> 00:26:17,309
- Hello, what place was Ye Xiaowen?
- I don't know.

372
00:26:18,519 --> 00:26:21,179
- Hello, what place was Ye Xiaowen?
- I don't know.

373
00:26:22,540 --> 00:26:25,800
Does anyone know what place Ye Xiaowen was?

374
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:28,380
Gao Yang!

375
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:42,419
I knew you would come.

376
00:26:49,900 --> 00:26:51,970
What place did you get?

377
00:26:53,380 --> 00:26:55,340
Second place.

378
00:26:55,979 --> 00:26:58,256
I can go to Beijing University of Technology now.

379
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:05,879
Gao Yang, are you happy in Beijing?

380
00:27:05,879 --> 00:27:07,219
Did you gain weight or lose weight?

381
00:27:07,219 --> 00:27:08,740
I think you've lost weight.

382
00:27:08,740 --> 00:27:10,519
Doesn't B-Beijing have good food?

383
00:27:10,519 --> 00:27:13,000
How are your grades? Have you improved?

384
00:27:13,000 --> 00:27:14,960
Did Anna and Zhan Chonghai mistreat you?

385
00:27:14,960 --> 00:27:16,952
No.

386
00:27:23,039 --> 00:27:24,780
Well, I'm alright.

387
00:27:24,780 --> 00:27:27,899
I'm relieved to see you guys. I have to go now.

388
00:27:27,899 --> 00:27:29,839
Don't go.

389
00:27:29,839 --> 00:27:32,536
Gao Yang.

390
00:27:32,536 --> 00:27:34,540
Gao Yang, you can't go.

391
00:27:39,300 --> 00:27:43,200
I know you don't want to go abroad at all.

392
00:27:45,660 --> 00:27:48,579
Weren't you the one who said to not make compromises?

393
00:27:48,579 --> 00:27:50,639
What are you doing now?

394
00:27:54,100 --> 00:27:57,601
Gao Yang, let's go.

395
00:27:59,659 --> 00:28:02,620
Well, take care of yourself.

396
00:28:04,140 --> 00:28:07,000
Auntie, I want to talk to you.

397
00:28:07,000 --> 00:28:08,820
I have nothing to say to you.

398
00:28:08,820 --> 00:28:11,463
Auntie! Auntie!

399
00:28:11,463 --> 00:28:13,219
What are you doing, Gao Bin?

400
00:28:13,219 --> 00:28:15,119
The boy says he wants to talk to you. Just talk to him.

401
00:28:15,119 --> 00:28:17,000
- I want to talk to you, too.
- I don't want to talk to you guys.

402
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:18,160
Then leave!

403
00:28:18,160 --> 00:28:19,640
Are you getting more shameless as you grow older?

404
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:22,340
So what? If you want to take him away, take my arm with you too!

405
00:28:22,340 --> 00:28:23,519
Go!

406
00:28:23,519 --> 00:28:25,079
Start the car!

407
00:28:25,079 --> 00:28:26,994
- Come on, guys!
- Auntie!

408
00:28:26,994 --> 00:28:29,519
- Auntie, I'm Beibei!
- Auntie!

409
00:28:29,519 --> 00:28:33,219
Please give them another chance, Auntie!

410
00:28:34,240 --> 00:28:36,180
- I beg you, Auntie!
- I beg of you! I beg you.

411
00:28:36,180 --> 00:28:38,147
That's enough!

412
00:28:55,380 --> 00:28:59,319
Jia Jia, what is Xiaowen planning to say?

413
00:29:00,039 --> 00:29:01,860
Xiaowen

414
00:29:02,380 --> 00:29:08,519
probably wants to pay her back in exchange for Gao Yang to come back home.

415
00:29:08,519 --> 00:29:10,833
Well, I have money.

416
00:29:10,833 --> 00:29:11,960
Let's put our money together.

417
00:29:11,960 --> 00:29:13,319
Put our money together.

418
00:29:13,319 --> 00:29:18,060
I have twenty, fifty,

419
00:29:24,680 --> 00:29:26,480
seventy-four. Seventy-four.

420
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:27,879
- A hundred and thirty-five.
- A hundred and thirty-five.

421
00:29:27,879 --> 00:29:31,300
That means a hundred and seventy-four plus thirty-five.

422
00:29:31,300 --> 00:29:35,340
- Thirty, thirty-two,
- Fifty-seven.

423
00:29:35,340 --> 00:29:38,079
That's a total of

424
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:39,839
two hundred and ninety-eight.

425
00:29:39,839 --> 00:29:40,839
That's about it.

426
00:29:40,839 --> 00:29:42,739
Would you like to order anything?

427
00:29:42,739 --> 00:29:43,920
Just serve us something.

428
00:29:43,920 --> 00:29:45,599
We're busy. Two hundred and ninety-eight.

429
00:29:45,599 --> 00:29:48,880
Our lowest meal standard is two hundred and ninety-eight per person.

430
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:51,060
Is that okay for you?

431
00:29:56,319 --> 00:30:01,720
Well, I think the minimum per person here is a bit low.

432
00:30:02,799 --> 00:30:06,268
- Let's go to another place.
- Sure.

433
00:30:13,240 --> 00:30:16,200
Well, you should eat or drink something, too. To calm down.

434
00:30:16,200 --> 00:30:18,359
I still have something else to do!

435
00:30:18,359 --> 00:30:20,475
Just be out with it.

436
00:30:27,939 --> 00:30:29,464
Auntie,

437
00:30:30,419 --> 00:30:34,719
I want to thank you for your donations on behalf of everyone at the orphanage.

438
00:30:36,780 --> 00:30:38,620
Thank you from the bottom of my heart.

439
00:30:38,620 --> 00:30:40,495
No need to thank me.

440
00:30:52,572 --> 00:30:56,915
[IOU: Ye Xiaowen borrows ¥400k from Ms. Anna for Sunshine Orphanage. Ye Xiaowen will make periodic repayments plus interest when he starts working.]

441
00:31:04,960 --> 00:31:07,078
I will

442
00:31:07,078 --> 00:31:08,979
surely pay you back.

443
00:31:09,799 --> 00:31:11,760
I don't have money now,

444
00:31:12,759 --> 00:31:14,939
but I will pay you back

445
00:31:15,440 --> 00:31:18,019
with interest when I start working.

446
00:31:19,599 --> 00:31:22,879
I hope you can respect Gao Yang's wishes

447
00:31:23,559 --> 00:31:25,734
and not force him to go abroad.

448
00:31:33,839 --> 00:31:36,200
Xiaowen, you don't have to pay her back.

449
00:31:36,200 --> 00:31:39,559
Xiaowen. I should be the one to pay her back.

450
00:31:39,559 --> 00:31:42,079
You helped me before. It's my turn to help you.

451
00:31:42,079 --> 00:31:43,580
Enough.

452
00:31:43,580 --> 00:31:46,760
Stop putting on an act here. I don't care about the money.

453
00:31:46,760 --> 00:31:51,515
Gao Yang, I already told you. I only care about your future.

454
00:31:51,515 --> 00:31:53,130
What should you do if you don't go abroad?

455
00:31:53,130 --> 00:31:56,540
You can ask him yourself. Can he get into a college?

456
00:31:57,359 --> 00:31:59,739
Going to college isn't the only way out.

457
00:31:59,739 --> 00:32:01,060
You also never went to college.

458
00:32:01,060 --> 00:32:02,659
Aren't you much better than me, a college graduate?

459
00:32:02,659 --> 00:32:05,000
Gao Bin, times have changed.

460
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:08,419
Even in my company, a college degree is the most basic requirement!

461
00:32:08,419 --> 00:32:11,860
If Gao Yang can't go to college, he'll be worse than you in the future.

462
00:32:11,860 --> 00:32:15,079
That's enough. We're all begging you now.

463
00:32:15,079 --> 00:32:17,059
Is your begging worth anything?

464
00:32:17,059 --> 00:32:18,319
Why are you being like this?

465
00:32:18,319 --> 00:32:21,039
- That's the way I am!
- Do you want to be hated for a good deed?

466
00:32:21,039 --> 00:32:24,079
I'm only concerned about my son's future! I don't care who you hate!

467
00:32:24,079 --> 00:32:25,459
You care about his future.

468
00:32:25,459 --> 00:32:27,039
Have you thought about his feelings?

469
00:32:27,039 --> 00:32:29,119
Have you ever listened to his own wishes? Does he want to go abroad?

470
00:32:29,119 --> 00:32:31,200
I don't care if he wants to or not. I'm doing this for his own good!

471
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:33,559
Are you treating your son as an employee? Why must he listen to you for everything?

472
00:32:33,559 --> 00:32:34,760
You won't even qualify to be my employee!

473
00:32:34,760 --> 00:32:36,928
- I don't care for it!
- Auntie,

474
00:32:38,140 --> 00:32:40,819
please listen to Gao Yang's own ideas.

475
00:32:40,819 --> 00:32:42,579
Do you have a say in this?

476
00:32:42,579 --> 00:32:44,699
- Watch the attitude.
- What about my attitude?

477
00:32:44,699 --> 00:32:46,760
Xiaowen and Gao Yang are brothers. We are family, you know?

478
00:32:46,760 --> 00:32:49,759
He's your family, not mine! She wasn't my first love!

479
00:32:49,759 --> 00:32:51,000
What are you saying in front of the kids?

480
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:52,668
- I...
- Stop fighting.

481
00:32:55,680 --> 00:32:57,659
I want to take the college entrance exam.

482
00:32:57,659 --> 00:32:59,000
What do you want to do?

483
00:32:59,000 --> 00:33:00,860
I want to take the college entrance exam.

484
00:33:00,860 --> 00:33:02,359
Can you pass it?

485
00:33:02,359 --> 00:33:06,480
Mom, don't you care about my future?

486
00:33:06,480 --> 00:33:08,739
I'll just get into a college then.

487
00:33:08,739 --> 00:33:10,800
Just let me try it.

488
00:33:13,160 --> 00:33:18,460
Let him try it. Besides, our country is developing nicely right now.

489
00:33:18,460 --> 00:33:19,820
Beijing is going to host the Olympic Games.

490
00:33:19,820 --> 00:33:21,339
Why should we go abroad?

491
00:33:21,339 --> 00:33:23,560
What's the point of going to a mediocre college?

492
00:33:23,560 --> 00:33:25,486
How about the Beijing University of Technology?

493
00:33:29,559 --> 00:33:33,219
Gao Yang, the Beijing University of Technology is a bit hard for you.

494
00:33:33,219 --> 00:33:36,000
A lot of their majors require a higher score than Tsinghua University.

495
00:33:36,000 --> 00:33:37,359
Let's choose another one.

496
00:33:37,359 --> 00:33:39,359
The Beijing University of Technology it is.

497
00:33:39,359 --> 00:33:43,280
If I get into the Beijing University of Technology, can I not go abroad?

498
00:34:10,057 --> 00:34:15,905
♫  I know the direction of dawn  ♫

499
00:34:15,905 --> 00:34:23,370
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

500
00:34:23,370 --> 00:34:29,360
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

501
00:34:29,360 --> 00:34:35,400
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

502
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:41,952
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

503
00:34:41,952 --> 00:34:47,692
